/* DEVELOPMENT IN SEX RATIOS							             */
/*-------------------------------------------------------------------*/

// prepares data for analysis
//preserve
keep round survey urban observation_age* mom_id b*_sex b*_born_cmc
reshape long b@_sex b@_born_cmc, i(mom_id) j(bo)
drop if b_sex == .
gen born_year = int((b_born_cmc-1)/12)+1900
